Interface JCL_CPfacade


  • public interface JCL_CPfacade
    Version:
    1.0 The developer API for capacity planning JCL adopts the concept of task cost, so the developer can obtain how a certain task costs in terms of runtime and memory consumption

    • Method Detail

      • getTaskTimes

        java.util.List<java.lang.Long> getTaskTimes(java.util.concurrent.Future<JCL_result> ticket)
        Get a list of times for task, representing its cost. The times are: 1- Request; 2- handle by Host; 3- Start executing or Send to a new Host; 4- Finishes the execution or handle by a new host 5 - leave the Host or Start execution; 6 - Arrive the result at client or or End execution; 7 - leave the new the Host; 8 - Arrive the result at client.
        Parameters:
        ticket - - task identification.
        Returns:
        A list of times in nanoseconds.
